Start and setup the approved project onto GitHub.

Source: R/admin.R
admin_start_approved_project.Rd

Start and setup the approved project onto GitHub.

Usage

admin_start_approved_project(user, proj_abbrev)

Arguments

user

The GitHub username.

proj_abbrev

The abbreviation for the project.

Value

Nothing, used for the side effects of making a project and setting up the GitHub repo.
